{"bio":null,"bio_l":"天界之王，众神之父，宙斯对待英雄一向视如己出。然而在无数次与凡间的女性幽会时当场被抓后，宙斯接到了妻子给他下的最后通牒：“既然你这么喜欢凡人，就去当凡人吧。如果你能证明的忠诚，就回来做我永生的丈夫。不然的话，就去和你的创造物一起去死吧。”宙斯无奈的发现她的逻辑（和她的魔法）无懈可击，只好照她说的去做。从那以后宙斯洗心革面，在凡人面前不再多情，将爱留给他永生的女神。但为了证明他配得上永恒的爱妻，他必须在战场上，大获全胜。","stats":"<img src=\"Int\" alt=\"Intelligence\" />Intelligence:20 + 2.70<br /><img src=\"Agi\" alt=\"Agility\" />Agility:11 + 1.20<br /><img src=\"Str\" alt=\"Strength\" />Strength:19 + 2.30<br /><img src=\"Attack\" alt=\"Damage\" />Damage:21 - 29<br /><img src=\"Speed\" alt=\"Movespeed\" />Movespeed:295<br /><img src=\"Defense\" alt=\"Armor\" />Armor:1.54","stats1":[["Int","Intelligence","20 + 2.70"],["Agi","Agility","11 + 1.20"],["Str","Strength","19 + 2.30"],["Attack","Damage","21 - 29"],["Speed","Movespeed","295"],["Defense","Armor","1.54"]],"detailstats":"<div class=\"redboxContent\"><div class=\"redboxTop\"></div><div id=\"statsInner\"><div id=\"statsLeft\"><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol\">25</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">15</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">1</div>等级</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,940</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,123</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">511</div>生命值</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,362</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">751</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">260</div>魔法值</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">126-134</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">79-87</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">41-49</div>攻击力</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">8</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">4</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">2</div>护甲</div></div><div id=\"statsRight\"><div class=\"statRow\"></div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1800 / 800</div>视野范围</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">350</div>攻击范围</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1100</div>弹道速度</div></div><br clear=\"both\" /></div><div class=\"redboxBottom\"></div></div>","detailstats1":[["生命值","1,940","1,123","5